tle_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Def.\">Def.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11</biblScope></bibl>, al. ; of angles, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">similar,</tr_> i.e. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">equal,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg005:296b:20\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Cael.\">Cael.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">296b20</biblScope></bibl>,<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg005:297b:19\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">297b19</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg005:311b:34\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">311b34</biblScope></bibl>, cf. Thalesap.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4036.tlg011:1p.251F\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Procl.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">in Euc.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1p.251F.</biblScope> </bibl> </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n73672.10\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> of Numbers, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">square,</tr_> the product of two equal factors, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2000.tlg001:6:2:21\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Plot.\">Plot.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.2.21</biblScope> </bibl> ; cf. <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀνόμοιος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2000.tlg001:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"B\" id=\"n73672.11\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> Construction : </sense> <sense n=\"1\" id=\"n73672.12\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> abs., freq. in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author></bibl>, etc. (v. supr.). </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n73672.13\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> c. dat. of the person or thing which another resembles : so always in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hes.\">Hes.</a></author></bibl>, and usu. in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> </bibl> and <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Att.\">Att.</a></gram> </gramGrp> (v. supr.) : but sts. c. gen., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τοῖσι τούτων ὁμοίοις χύμασι</foreign> <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">v.l. in</abbr> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0627.tlg010.perseus-grc1:12\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hp.\">Hp.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Art.\">Art.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12</biblScope> </bibl> (Diels<tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">Ztschr.f.vergl.</tr_> <pb n=\"1225\" TEIform=\"pb\"/> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">Sprachf.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">47.200</biblScope> </bibl>), <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">v.</abbr> l. in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:37\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.37</biblScope> </bibl> and <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg030.perseus-grc1:472d\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ R.\">R.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">472d</biblScope> </bibl> ; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τουτέων