Iform=\"foreign\">οὔ τις ὁμοῖα νοήματα Πηνελοπείῃ ᾔδη,</foreign> for <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τοῖς τῆς Πηνελοπείης,</foreign> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:2:121\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.121</biblScope> </bibl> : also in Prose, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἅρματα ὅ. ἐκείνῳ,</foreign> for <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τοῖς ἐκείνου,</foreign> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg007.perseus-grc1:6:1:50\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Cyr.\">Cyr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.1.50</biblScope> </bibl> ; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὁμοίαν ταῖς δούλαις ἐσθῆτα,</foreign> for <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τῇ τῶν δουλῶν,</foreign> ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg007.perseus-grc1:5:1:4\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.1.4</biblScope> </bibl> ; cf. <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἴσος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg007.perseus-grc1:1:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.1</biblScope></bibl></cit>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">συγγενής</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg007.perseus-grc1:111:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">111.2</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n73672.15\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> c. acc. of that in which a person or thing resembles another, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀθανάτῃσι φυὴν καὶ εἶδος ὁμοίη</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:6:16\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TE